title: Vampire the Masquerade - Clanbooks Complete
description:
As near to a complete set of VTM Clanbooks as I have been able to assemble. Includes original and revised versions of the main clans, as well as the various bloodlines.

Salubri

Toreador (both)
Tremere (both)
Tzimisce (both)
Ventrue (both)
